OL,3,CCharities warn of closures due to hike
OL,4,Cin National Insurance
OL,6,FThe charity sector says rises in
OL,7,FNational Insurance payments for
OL,8,Femployers will cost it more than #1
OL,9,Fbillion, as ITV News Consumer Editor
OL,10,FChris Choi reports
OL,12,FThere are new warnings of charity shop
OL,13,Fclosures and good causes having to cut
OL,14,Fvital services.
OL,16,FThe sector says rises in National
OL,17,FInsurance will cost it more than a
OL,18,Fbillion pounds. The chancellor has
OL,19,Ftold them she's faced tough choices,
OL,20,Fbut the latest charity appeal is to
OL,21,Fthe government.
