OL,3,CCharities warn of closures due to hike
OL,4,Cin National Insurance
OL,6,FResearch from 400 charities by Charity
OL,7,FFinance Group, which was given to ITV
OL,8,FNews, says 87% are now concerned about
OL,9,Fbeing able to afford the higher
OL,10,FNational Insurance.
OL,12,FThe sector predicts it will cost
OL,13,Fcharities #1.4 billion, with Marie
OL,14,FCurie estimating it will cost them
OL,15,Falone #2.9m.
OL,17,FMeanwhile, 27% of organisations
OL,18,Frunning charity shops say the likely
OL,19,Fimpact will be closures, according to
OL,20,FCharity Retail Association.
