OL,6,FSamira Najim, who receives support
OL,7,Ffrom a charity, said: "These
OL,8,Ffacilities rely on fundraising and it
OL,9,Fjust puts them in a terrible position
OL,10,Fand we really don't want to lose or
OL,11,Fsee any cuts to this service."
