OL,3,CCharities warn of closures due to hike
OL,4,Cin National Insurance
OL,6,FMichelle King, CEO of Little Miracles
OL,7,FCharity, which helps 50,000 families
OL,8,Fthat have children with life-limiting
OL,9,Fdisabilities, told ITV News: "It is
OL,10,Fgoing to cost us a minimum of
OL,11,F#24,000... we're a small local charity
OL,12,Fwith about 670 volunteers so to find
OL,13,Fan extra #24,000 is so hard and we're
OL,14,Fdoing all we can to avoid cutting
OL,15,Fservices."
OL,17,FThe government says it faced tough
OL,18,Fchoices but assured that half of
OL,19,Forganisations will pay no more in
OL,20,FNational Insurance.
