OL,4,Cin National Insurance
OL,6,FClare Mills from the Charity Finance
OL,7,FGroup is far from reassured, saying:
OL,8,F"What's gonna be really difficult for
OL,9,Fthe very large charities is many of
OL,10,Fthem having to look at recruitment
OL,11,Ffreezes or even in the worst case
OL,12,Fscenario redundancies and the people
OL,13,Fwho are going to feel the impact are
OL,14,Fthe people and communities who rely on
OL,15,Fthe service and support those
OL,16,Fcharities provide."
