OL,3,CCharities warn of closures due to hike
OL,4,Cin National Insurance
OL,6,FThe government says it values
OL,7,Fcharities and there are grants and
OL,8,Fsupport worth more than #900m, but
OL,9,Fmany good causes which exist to help
OL,10,Fothers - now say they need help.
OL,12,FJon Sparkes, CEO of Mencap, said:
OL,13,F"National Insurance contribution
OL,14,Fchanges will cost approximately #7
OL,15,Fmillion as an organisation. I'm really
OL,16,Fworried about 60 of our services and
OL,17,Fthose services provide support for
OL,18,Fmore than 230 people and employ some
OL,19,F400 people."
